        cost - the laptop's cost
        manufacturer - the laptop's manufacturer
        brand - the laptop's brand
        maxVolt - the laptop's maximum allowed input voltage
        maxWatt - the laptop's maximum power consumption
        operatingSystem - the laptop's operating system
        cpuType - the laptop's cpu type
        ramCapacity - the laptop's ram capacity
        HDDCapacity - the laptop's hdd capacity
